# vlc

> Cross-platform multimedia player
> More information: https://wiki.videolan.org/Documentation:Command_line/

- Play a file:

`vlc {file value}`

- Play in fullscreen:

`vlc --fullscreen {file value}`

- Play muted:

`vlc --no-audio {file value}`

- Play repeatedly:

`vlc --loop {file value}`

- Play video from a URL:

`vlc {string value: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oHg5SJYRHA0}`
